OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Sainsbury's asks    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff to delay Christmas   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fparties                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sainsbury's has asked workers to       
OL,6, postpone their Christmas parties until 
OL,7, the new year following the emergence of
OL,8, the Omicron Covid variant.             
OL,10,FThe supermarket said the situation was 
OL,11,F"very delicate", adding "we need to do 
OL,12,Feverything we can to make Christmas    
OL,13,Fsafe" for staff and customers.         
OL,15,FSainsbury's boss Simon Roberts said the
OL,16,Ffirm "will make sure no-one is out of  
OL,17,Fpocket as a result of this decision".  
OL,19,FOther businesses are choosing to scale 
OL,20,Fback festive gatherings this year.     
